                    NOTICES:
CURSOR CONTROL:
   With the PS/2 & BUS type mouse interfaces, the keyboard mouse-emulation
has been disabled.

COVOX CARD and the PS/2 MOUSE:
   If you are using a PS/2 type mouse interface, you cannot use the COVOX card
with SimCity.

TERRAIN EDITOR:
   If you order the TERRAIN EDITOR, please make sure you specify which size
disk you require.


